 272:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM55_NTZ/non_secure/port.c ****  * Bit[0] - 1 --> The exception was taken to the Secure state.
 273:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM55_NTZ/non_secure/port.c ****  */
