 282:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM55_NTZ/non_secure/port.c ****  *
 283:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM55_NTZ/non_secure/port.c ****  * Bit[6] - 0 --> The exception was taken from the Non-Secure state.
