 287:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM55_NTZ/non_secure/port.c ****  * Bit[2] - 1 --> Restore registers from the process stack.
 288:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM55_NTZ/non_secure/port.c ****  * Bit[1] - 0 --> Reserved, 0.
 289:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM55_NTZ/non_secure/port.c ****  * Bit[0] - 0 --> The exception was taken to the Non-Secure state.
 290:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM55_NTZ/non_secure/port.c ****  */
 291:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM55_NTZ/non_secure/port.c ****     #define portINITIAL_EXC_RETURN    ( 0xffffffbc )
